CustomField.description: If address part fields are used, concatenate them into a single string.
CustomField.formula: IF(MUSW__Street2__c != "", IF( MUSW__Street_Number__c != "",MUSW__Street_Number__c & " ","") & IF( MUSW__Street_Direction__c != "",MUSW__Street_Direction__c & " ","") & MUSW__Street2__c & IF(MUSW__Street_Suffix__c != ""," " & MUSW__Street_Suffix__c,"") & IF( MUSW__Unit__c != "", " " & IF(MUSW__Unit_Type__c != "", MUSW__Unit_Type__c & " ", "#") & MUSW__Unit__c,""), Name)
CustomField.label: Address
